        }
   ```
   
   Ensure this break condition is tracked distinctly in the test setup and
   runtime expectations to differentiate normal iteration end from unexpected
   behavior.
   
   #### Thorough Fix:
   Extend exception handling in the project so that the `be_stop_iteration` or
   `stop_iteration` case is clearly marked and isolated, informing calling
   functions of its occurrence as a logical, non-error action. This may involve
   revisiting exception throw logic in `src/be_api.c` and other modules adopting
   iterative or exception raising strategies to comprehensively record and
   address these cases consistently.

